text: David William Downing (born 6 October 1969) is an English former professional footballer who played as a striker in the Football League for York City, and in non-League football for Goole Town. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:People from Bideford Category:English footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:York City F.C. players Category:Goole Town F.C. players Category:English Football League players
